name: Oval Glass Opal Necklace
description:
A beautiful glass opal necklace! An oval pink vintage glass opal cabochon rests in a raw brass setting and hangs from an a 14k gold filled chain. When the light hits this necklace it's magic! The opal pendant sparkles and shines and shows flecks of pink, gold, blue...You will treasure this gorgeous piece of jewelry forever!

-The pink oval fire opal glass cabochon is 14x10mm in size and vintage! ATTENTION: This is NOT a real "opal stone" mined from the earth- it is a synthetic, man-made "glass cabochon" made to look similar to an opal stone.

-You will not receive the exact glass opal in the picture. Every one is slightly different but it adds to their vintage character.

-The flat cable chain is 14k GOLD-FILLED and so is the lobster clasp and all the findings. "Gold filled" is the next best thing to actual gold. It won't tarnish! It's dainty and super sparkly!

-You can choose the LENGTH of the necklace you would like in the drop-down menu to your right.

-Comes sweetly gift wrapped in a Kraft jewelry box just for you!
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 
*DO NOT WEAR THIS NECKLACE WHILE SWIMMING, SHOWERING OR DOING RIGOROUS ACTIVITY- IT'S VERY, VERY DELICATE!

name: Ball Jar Happy Holidays Cards
description:
**I'm bringing these back for the 2013 holiday season!!! They are new and improved! ~Enjoy!~**

**ATTENTION: Whatever HEART color you choose I will give you the OPPOSITE color for the envelope. If you want the same color envelope as the heart then please send me a message.

-Love them but need a different quantity? Just send me a message and ask for a custom order!

*The DondaLee's logo & website address are printed on the back of every card.

*Objects in photos not included*
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
||HISTORY OF THE CARDS ||

I first started making these cards in October of 2012 to match my original ball jar cards! For 2013 I've made some changes: they are now printed on premium recycled Kraft paper and the designs are entirely printed as opposed to stamped. name: Pastel Fabric & Ribbon Garland
description:
**I've got another one in the works and will hopefully have it in the shop in a few weeks!**
---------------------------------------------
A gorgeous, one-of-a-kind ribbon garland! I handmade this special garland in hopes that it would find a good home. It was a true labor of love! I first made a ribbon garland for my own studio and I really wanted to make another for someone else to enjoy!

Perfect to use for:
-A photo prop
-Your craft space/studio
-Your office
-Your wedding
-And much more! 

-The garland measures: 4.5 ft from one end of where the fabric starts to the other. If you include the Jute twine that it's strung on the total length is 6.5.

-The rope is made of rustic "Jute" twine.

-The ribbons are a mixture of vintage fabrics, new designer fabrics, new gold sparkle ribbon and new pastel ribbons. It is MOSTLY made of vintage fabrics. Each fabric strip was hand torn and tied by me. I wanted it to have an old, rustic look. The fabrics I used are beautiful pastels, shabby chic roses, yellow and blue plaid, pastel silk ribbons in aqua, pink, yellow and mint and lovely gold sparkle ribbons.

-The ribbons are packed tightly together to give the garland a very full look. You could always spread the ribbons apart if you wanted to make the garland even longer.

*This garland is one of a kind!

*I will only be shipping this particular item to the United States due to it's weight.

~I hope you treasure it always!~
